Subject: RFID Implant Demo with Q&A
Description: Have you ever thought about getting an RFID chip or a magnet implanted in your hand so you can interact with computers or even feel electricity? Featured Guests Dangerous Things offer a demo of an RFID Implant and answer your questions about biohacking and how it can work for you.  Speakers include:Amal Graafstra, Anita Fowler - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none

Subject: The Future of Biohacking
Description: Featured Guests Dangerous Things look into the future to discuss how we could incorporate new technology into our bodies. Biohacks, nootropics, and nutrition will be explored in this discussion.  Speakers include:Amal Graafstra, Anita Fowler - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
